---
title: Lemon-Garlic Shrimp, Corn and Peppers with Roasted Potatoes
description: This family-friendly feast will whisk you away on a trip to the Deep South. We've packed in all the flavours of a classic shrimp boil, including lemon, butter and garlic. Better yet, it all comes together on 2 baking sheets for easy clean-up!
